', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/144567/', '', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, More', 'Clevidipine, Mibefradil, Celecoxib', 1767369485);
